: 1325.718, "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 14654652, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-3060059034199589v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by erin.gunzelman", "description": "go ask a frog what day of the week it is, then comment and tell me what you think 😉🙃 really! because i don’t have all the answers, this is just me having fun \n\nor join my patreon where we can discuss this + lots of other topics (and how they relate to our personal experience of physical reality) during our SOUL SYMPOSIUM gatherings\n\ncomment TIME and i’ll send the link \n\niloveyou 🫶🏼✨#consciousness #dinosaursex #quantumphysics #tartaria", "duration": 88.433, "timestamp": 1761475892, "uploader_id": "46282704586", "uploader": "erin gunzelman", "channel": "erin.gunzelman", "like_count": 23998, "comment_count": 810, "comments": [{"author": "ahmeddabdelrahemm", "author_id": "2234623684", "id": "17940826293140677", "text": "Thank you ❤️", "timestamp": 1773309126}, {"author": "natalie_a_hardy", "author_id": "1464310663", "id": "17951340417102305", "text": "Time", "timestamp": 1772787181}, {"author": "austin.stallan", "author_id": "3608933672", "id": "18058024850681017", "text": "go check out @maryisalien video", "timestamp": 1772344352}, {"author": "paul.e.humphries", "author_id": "45709161429", "id": "18039759989757422", "text": "What I would love is if we could get back in tune with the cycles of the earth and the moon. Rearranged the months of the year as well as the number of days in them so our rhythms and harmony would be restored.", "timestamp": 1772333631}, {"author": "thecapitolachristy", "author_id": "4052245044", "id": "18110669032674779", "text": "The SKYCLOCK MOVES. Time is absolutely an entity.", "timestamp": 1772151890}, {"author": "hotcheetosandsunglasses", "author_id": "62169777288", "id": "18088192736133676", "text": "I got kicked out of my 8th grade class because I’m told my teacher time isn’t real and that it’s an illusion. We went back and forth, he got pissed, I got kicked out 😂🤷🏽‍♂️", "timestamp": 1772142230}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/572132412_18061624640536587_5352090607479641209_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p640x640_sh0.08_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4xMzIweDIzNDguc2RyLmY4Mjc4Ny5kZWZhdWx0X2NvdmVyX2ZyYW1lLmMyIn0&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=103&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gF6gXA3VJCfCiPOoPPr3ZY6hTH-2lUYCUizxOVZcEMpe5jhS-LIaflgcShqMWYq2nE&_nc_ohc=9KIoY0fSWSUQ7kNvwFMlwge&_nc_gid=hUS4ohdI2qDB2noxGcPjIQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af1B_xB1qffWr4H_j0UlVtQkwcqDOPvOxQbwSR6ZP2wuzg&oe=69D4BA5D&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1138, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1138"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/572132412_18061624640536587_5352090607479641209_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p750x750_sh0.08_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4xMzIweDIzNDguc2RyLmY4Mjc4Ny5kZWZhdWx0X2NvdmVyX2ZyYW1lLmMyIn0&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=103&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gF6gXA3VJCfCiPOoPPr3ZY6hTH-2lUYCUizxOVZcEMpe5jhS-LIaflgcShqMWYq2nE&_nc_ohc=9KIoY0fSWSUQ7kNvwFMlwge&_nc_gid=hUS4ohdI2qDB2noxGcPjIQ&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af2-KgrLMaloWBnfVsjfYvftXqZrLV3hiFPg2FQ1wKmE8g&oe=69D4BA5D&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1334, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1334"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/572132412_18061624640536587_5352090607479641209_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh0.08_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4xMzIweDIzNDguc2RyLmY4Mjc4Ny5kZWZhdWx0X2NvdmVyX2ZyYW1lLmMyIn0&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=103&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gF6g